✅ 7) Access Keys बनाईं
User `student` open किया
Security credentials tab
Access keys → Create access key
Use case: Command Line Interface (CLI)
Create access key
.csv download किया
Access Key ID + Secret Key सुरक्षित रखा
---
✅ 8) AWS CLI Configure किया
Command run:
```cmd
aws configure --profile student
```
Values entered:
AWS Access Key ID
AWS Secret Access Key
Default region: ap-south-1 (या us-east-1)
Output format: json
---
✅ 9) Configuration Verify किया
Command run:
```cmd
aws configure list --profile student
```
Output को notes में paste किया
